                {
                    "name": "Vanth Scythes",
                    "type": "sidebar",
                    "text": "Vanths' favored weapon is the <a aonid=\"39\" game-obj=\"Weapons\">scythe</a>, a choice that even further adds to their fearsome appearance and can lead to unfortunate associations with the <a aonid=\"250\" game-obj=\"Monsters\">Grim Reaper</a> or <a aonid=\"19\" game-obj=\"Deities\">Urgathoa</a> among more superstitious mortals. Vanths find such comparisons to be ignorant at best or insulting at worst. Some vanths infuse their scythes with different qualities, such as <a aonid=\"375\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">cold iron</a> or <a aonid=\"379\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">silver</a>, depending on the nature of their most common enemies.",
