                        "text": "DC 22; <b>5th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"69\" game-obj=\"Spells\">dimension door</a></u></i>; <b>4th</b><i><u><a aonid=\"69\" game-obj=\"Spells\">dimension door</a></u></i> (at will); <b>3rd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"173\" game-obj=\"Spells\">locate</a></u></i> (\u00d73), <i><u><a aonid=\"269\" game-obj=\"Spells\">searing light</a></u></i> (\u00d73); <b>2nd</b><i><u><a aonid=\"164\" game-obj=\"Spells\">invisibility</a></u></i> (at will; self only)<br/>",
