                    {
                        "name": "Infuse Weapon",
                        "type": "offensive_action",
                        "text": "A vanth's scythe is its symbol of office and gains a measure of its personal power. This scythe becomes a <i>+1 scythe</i> and is treated as if it were <a aonid=\"374\" game-obj=\"Equipment\">adamantine</a> while the vanth wields it. A vanth whose scythe is taken or destroyed can infuse a new one with an hour of work.",
